Package psidev.psi.mi.jami.xml.cache

Class InMemoryIdentityObjectCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.xml.cache.InMemoryIdentityObjectCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PsiXmlObjectCache
    public class InMemoryIdentityObjectCache
extends Object
implements PsiXmlObjectCache
    It keeps a in memory cache of objects having an id. The cache is based on a in memory Identity map.
    Since:
    12/11/13
